data.description: Opportunity awaits on this charming Woodland Park townhome with stunning Pikes Peak views! Nestled in a tranquil and serene setting, this end-unit gem offers all the comforts of a peaceful small-town atmosphere with the added bonus of having access to fantastic hiking and off-roading trails right at your fingertips. No HOA fees provide you with unmatched freedom and flexibility. The front yard features a perennial garden, while the backyard boasts a vegetable and flower garden, ensuring you can enjoy fresh summer veggies and the beauty of nature at all times. Inside, discover a delightful open floor plan that has been thoughtfully updated with modern touches. All new exterior siding, fresh interior and exterior paint, new stainless-steel appliances, refreshed bathrooms, fixtures, plush upstairs carpeting, new vinyl plank flooring, hardware/doorknobs, upgraded storage and fresh paint inside and out. Enjoy the custom built-out pantry with ample storage for culinary needs. Main-level open floor plan is great for entertaining or everyday living, and the cozy wood stove with brick surround offers nice ambience and plenty of warmth all winter long. Upstairs, find 2 generous-sized bedrooms that share a full bath breathtaking onyx stone panels giving it a luxurious and elegant design. The fully fenced backyard has space for you dogs, a play set for the kids, AMAZING perennial garden for the green thumb, and still has room for whole family BBQs. 1-car attached garage for secured parking and convenient off-street parking along the side of home. Experience the joy of living in a central location, beautiful updated features, and the breathtaking view of Pikes Peak. Welcome home! 4 virtually staged photos used in this listing.
